isio、Keynote 等输出的文档方便传输、阅读、版本维护等，现在适合自己及团队的工具就好。","like_count":4},{"had_liked":false,"id":874,"user_name":"听天由己","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c1","uid":1019531,"ip_address":"","ucode":"59BC32324B88C5","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/0f/8e/8b/38b93ca0.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1511409689,"is_pvip":false,"discussion_count":0,"race_medal":0,"score":"18691278873","product_id":100002601,"comment_content":"这些工具大部分都尝试，可惜 Mac 上的工具现在才开始了解，还是相对落后不少。<br><br>对于初稿，我更倾向于直接用纸笔，在淘宝上直接买了一套手绘纸，然后就开始了，一直以来都没注意对手稿的保存，这一方面真的改进了。<br><br>对于原型，以我个人为例，现在在小公司创业，常见的做法是在手绘与流程图大致确认后，直接和 UI 同事一起设计，相互补充，共同讨论，不喜欢用原型工具，除非一定要正式讨论。虽然画原型是产品经理的日常工作，但是术业有专攻，我更希望把时间利用起来。凡事都要以目标与效率为依据，工具真的是次要的。<br><br>最后就是，体验新产品与保持习惯需要我们学会取舍，我喜欢文章中的这句话：工具是为我们服务的，不要成为它的奴隶。","like_count":5},{"had_liked":false,"id":865,"user_name":"天才小菜头","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c1","uid":1020631,"ip_address":"","ucode":"EE9EF9F17B46FE","user_header":"http://thirdwx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/vi_32/s7Pz1jCQFsSOMtMYlsHpMnKwOg0icibRqtnlwdlBww4QWpwRIGbaTRc6gNLsykE9ApuDRI8n1Rtrth244odlkM6Q/132","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1511396099,"is_pvip":false,"discussion_count":1,"race_medal":0,"score":"18691265283","product_id":100002601,"comment_content":"balsamiq 是那种手绘风格的原型，飞常讨喜，不过交互方面就做的不够，比笔纸画出来标准一点","like_count":4,"discussions":[{"author":{"id":1033219,"avatar":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/0f/c4/03/f753fda7.jpg","nickname":"JianXu","note":"","ucode":"2A61BDBB573BDC","race_medal":0,"user_type":1,"is_pvip":false},"reply_author":{"id":0,"avatar":"","nickname":"","note":"","ucode":"","race_medal":0,"user_type":1,"is_pvip":false},"discussion":{"id":332444,"discussion_content":"有 balsamiq cloud 的","likes_number":0,"is_delete":false,"is_hidden":false,"ctime":1607222299,"is_liked":false,"can_delete":false,"is_complain":false,"is_top":false,"parent_id":0,"ip_address":""},"score":2,"extra":"","child_discussion_number":0,"child_discussions":[]}]},{"had_liked":false,"id":7796